The paper discusses security solutions for V2X communication technology, which involves the networking of vehicles and infrastructure units. This falls under the category of computer security (cs.CR) and networked systems (cs.NI). The paper also discusses optimizing security solutions while considering network requirements, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY). Finally, the paper presents a threat analysis for V2X enabling technologies, which falls under cyber security (cs.CY).
